OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782913702
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's brother says killer
OL,4,Cshould never be freed
OL,6,FStephen McCullagh's appeal against his
OL,7,Fsentence for Natalie McNally's murder
OL,8,Fis "retraumatising" and he should
OL,9,Fnever be released, her brother has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FDeclan McNally was reacting after it
OL,13,Femerged McCullagh has launched a legal
OL,14,Fbid against the 31-year minimum jail
OL,15,Fterm he received for killing his
OL,16,Fpregnant partner in December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
