PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782913702
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's brother says killer
OL,4,Cshould never be freed
OL,6,FHe said: "It's just another blow. My
OL,7,Fmum and dad, they're strong and
OL,8,Fresilient people. We shouldn't have to
OL,9,Fbe so strong again and again and
OL,10,Fagain, it's just completely
OL,11,Fretraumatising the whole family.
OL,13,F"It just speaks to the character of
OL,14,Fthe murderer, the way he's acted
OL,15,Fbefore, during, and after the murder,
OL,16,Fafter the trial, you just expect the
OL,17,Fcomplete worst from that individual.
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782913702
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's brother says killer
OL,4,Cshould never be freed
OL,6,F"He hasn't shown any remorse, no
OL,7,Fregret, no responsibility, and now
OL,8,Fhe's going to court again, looking to
OL,9,Freduce sentence. It's astonishing."
OL,11,FMcCullagh, 36, of Woodland Gardens,
OL,12,FLisburn, faked a YouTube gaming
OL,13,Flivestream in an effort to provide an
OL,14,Falibi for the murder of Ms McNally at
OL,15,Fher home in Lurgan.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
