FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782913702
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's brother says killer
OL,4,Cshould never be freed
OL,6,FA postmortem found Ms McNally had
OL,7,Fsuffered a "prolonged assault" that
OL,8,Fincluded multiple stab wounds,
OL,9,Fstrangulation and blows to the head.
OL,10,FMcCullagh was told by a judge at
OL,11,FBelfast Crown Court in June that he
OL,12,Fwill serve at least 31 years in prison
OL,13,Ffor the killing after being found
OL,14,Fguilty by a jury.
OL,16,FThe Public Prosecution Service has
OL,17,Fsince been notified that an appeal
OL,18,Fagainst the sentence has now been
OL,19,Flodged
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
