PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782913702
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's brother says killer
OL,4,Cshould never be freed
OL,6,FMr McNally told the BBC Good Morning
OL,7,FUlster programme that the PPS had
OL,8,Fcalled his family on Monday to notify
OL,9,Fthem about the appeal.
OL,11,FMr McNally said it was another "knock"
OL,12,Ffor the family, which would now have
OL,13,Fto wait to find out when the appeal
OL,14,Fhearing will take place.
OL,16,FHe said: "My dad said last night,
OL,17,Fwe're watching the World Cup, Natalie
OL,18,Fwas murdered the night of the last
OL,19,FWorld Cup final, and here we are
OL,20,Fwatching the next World Cup and we're
OL,21,Fstill getting news about court.
OL,26,@sD@`OUsD@fO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782913702
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's brother says killer
OL,4,Cshould never be freed
OL,6,F"We sort of hoped that after
OL,7,Fsentencing, that we would have the
OL,8,Fspace and time and calmness to be able
OL,9,Fto grieve in a more proper way, but
OL,10,Fthat's less likely now with this
OL,11,Fappeal."
OL,13,FMr McNally said McCullagh's sentence
OL,14,Fshould be increased, rather than
OL,15,Freduced. He added: "He hasn't shown an
OL,16,Founce of remorse.
OL,18,F"I don't know if he views (it) as some
OL,19,Fsort of free hit ` why not just have
OL,20,Fan appeal if he's nothing to lose?
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]wD@TOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782913702
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's brother says killer
OL,4,Cshould never be freed
OL,6,F"But it's not a free hit for our
OL,7,Ffamily, we're back in the court
OL,8,Fprocess worrying. It will be hanging
OL,9,Fover us again.
OL,11,F"In my opinion, sentence should be
OL,12,Fgoing up. In my opinion, the person
OL,13,Fshould never be released."
